This vignette demonstrates how to create interactive maps using the leaflet package in R to visualize the gambling neighbourhoods identified using an hybrid approach combining HDBSCAN clustering with a fixed eps=500m specifically for London. Check the main vignette HDBSCAN_eps500 for general details about the methodology and the approach used.
